{"tid":1614489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重要】SHA512身份保護法","createTime":"2019-10-02T20:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T13:13:00.000Z","uid":223260,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0a3ddaedf4a12da75c790d34fe39923c8025d760","tid":1614489,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T20:14:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為保證閣下身份不被盜用，可以每次夢遊前提供一個SHA512 checksum，以供往後證明閣下身份。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1.Android用戶請下載hash droid（或其他閣下相信嘅hash計算機）<br />\n<br />\n2.選擇SHA 512<br />\n<br />\n3.輸入密碼<br />\n（請選擇足夠複雜且能記得的密碼！如使用中文字作為密碼，請注意異體字，不同輸入法可能有字體差異）<br />\n<br />\n複製checksum貼上論壇/社交平台：<br />\n<br />\na0a82a5122a497640b883917ade8e521fbd36239931732ffac441659746547b078779292f2af96b7f9f6dc3bc00542919c432283d77d36819979d5c0888fb675<br />\n<br />\n只有閣下知道密碼，只有閣下可以提供密碼予其他網友進行解碼，以證明閣下為閣下本人，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>而非被綁架或被殺後手機被盜用。</strong></span>（請牢記密碼！忘記密碼冇人幫到你！）<br />\n<br />\n以上checksum例子的密碼：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n各位可以將密碼輸入hash droid，檢查密碼是否一致。<br />\n<br />\n每次揭曉密碼後，請順帶提供下一個checksum。"},{"pid":"9fde12567b1577eb6a326ee431bff58d8a21617c","tid":1614489,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T22:41:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4177b5e431687bcb4c4abfae96ab6ef2e700f0f0","tid":1614489,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:17:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b335002acdbeefa2a02e519bc643a9ab696a1ca2","tid":1614489,"uid":26419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:19:05.000Z","msg":"睇唔明 不過推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2567960c7d84bee58031613d5dec68c798f3de","tid":1614489,"uid":30067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b335002acdbeefa2a02e519bc643a9ab696a1ca2","tid":1614489,"uid":26419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23: